.:: Zebra puzzle ::.
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: mystery, horror, crime, scientific, martial-arts
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: azalea, daffodil, bellflower, sunflower, lily
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-gold, kools, chesterfields, lucky-strike, parliaments
House: tower, palace, art-deco, victorian, futuristic
5 different pets are kept: dog, fox, zebra, horse, snails

1. the person who growsazalea is the person watching mystery movies
2. the person who growsdaffodil is the owner of the dog
3. the tower house is the person watching horror movies
4. the person who growsbellflower is the palace house
5. the person watching horror movies is to the right of the person watching crime movies
6. the old-gold-smoker is the owner of the snails
7. the kools-smoker is the person watching scientific movies
8. the art-deco house is in the middle
9. the person who growssunflower is on the far left
10. the chesterfields-smoker is on the left or right of the owner of the fox
11. the kools-smoker is to the left or right of the owner of the horse
12. the lucky-strike-smoker is the victorian house
13. the person who growslily is the parliaments-smoker
14. the person who growssunflower is to the left or right of the person watching martial-arts movies

.:: Answer ::.
|		|       1	|	2	|	3 	|	4	|	5	|
| Flower	|   sunflower	|    bellflower	|     azalea	|    daffodil	|    lily	|
| Movie-Genre		|    scientific	|      martial-arts	|      mystery	|     crime	|     horror	|
| House	|     futuristic	|      palace	|      art-deco	| victorian	|     tower	|
| Cigar		|     kools	| chesterfield	|    olg-gold	| lucky-strike	|   parliament	|
| Pet		|     fox	|     horse	|     snails	|     dog	|     zebra	|
